# SMTP Gmail (WAJIB App Password, bukan password login):
# 1. Aktifkan 2-Step Verification di Google Account
# 2. Buat App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. SMTP_PASS = 16 karakter (spasi boleh, akan di-strip otomatis)
# 4. Tes: npm run email:test
# 5. Kirim percobaan: TEST_EMAIL=anda@gmail.com npm run email:test -- --send
SMTP_HOST="smtp.gmail.com"
SMTP_PORT="587"
SMTP_SECURE="false"
SMTP_USER=""
SMTP_PASS=""
